1 Year of the Crown 👑✨

It wasn’t just a title — it was a rebirth.
From being a mom to embracing my vitiligo with pride, this journey wasn’t perfect, but it was powerful.
I’ve learned that no label — not “mom”, not “flawed”, not “busy” — can ever limit your worth or your dreams.
Because the real crown isn’t made of rhinestones… it’s made of resilience.

I’ll forever be grateful to the people who saw something in me — who recognised my light, my strength, and gave me the crown that changed everything.

Authentic 50K 🧿
As I’ve always believed, dreams do come true—and here it stands before you. 

@officialshraddhavadalia Winner Mrs World International 2024 🧿👑

I am utterly speechless, overwhelmed with emotions and at a loss of words.🥹

What greater gift could one ask for than to be celebrated for their true essence?😇

I owe this entirely to my upbringing and the unwavering support of my entire Vadalia family. It’s a blessing to be the part of the family that wants you to grow and achieve new heights everyday. 💝

Special thanks to my husband, @ankit.vadalia , for encouraging me to pursue my dreams and standing by my side always.❤️

How can I forget my sister from another mother, @krishna_patel__vadalia for always being there for me? Balancing home and work is no easy feat, and without your support, this achievement would not have been possible.✨

Not to forget my Little one , who dreams of my success more than me. This crown means much more to him. I am glad I could do this for him.🌻💝

My deepest gratitude to @glamourgurgaon and @mrsworldinternational for presenting this phenomenal platform to reveal my authentic self and for bestowing upon me this prestigious crown.
I am profoundly thankful to Mrs. @@barkhanangiaofficial @bnangia for your empowering support. To be crowned by the queen maker herself surpasses my wildest dreams.💕

A heartfelt thank you to all my mentors. I have never encountered a team with such dedication and unity, working like valiant soldiers, elevating Glamour Gurgaon as their own family. I am honored to now be part of this extraordinary family.✨❤️

#mrsworldinternational2024 #pageant2024 #glamourgurgaon #achievement #winner #achievinggoals #dreams #manifestingdreams #sucessstory

“How do you manage it all?”
I get this question a lot. Truth is , growth doesn’t pause real life.

Between reels and routines, there’s grocery bags, birthday balloons, unexpected guests, late-night laughs, temple prayers, and being a daughter, daughter-in-law, friend, and full-time mama , all at once.

These are the pictures that rarely make it to Instagram, but they hold my real story.
It’s not just about self-growth. It’s about showing up , even when it’s tough.
And somehow, we do. With love, with grace, and with just enough chaos.

Paisa wasool👇

💰 Budget-friendly? Hmm… ₹1200 – not exactly.
🧽 Soft jelly feel? No, it’s firmer than expected.
🎨 Good pigment? Yes, but only after layering.
🌿 Natural finish? Absolutely. Skin-like and fresh.
🔄 Need a buildup? Yes, one swipe won’t cut it.
🕒 Long-lasting? Not really. Touch-ups needed.
✨ Bonus? Adds a dewy glow — like a blush + gloss combo.
🔁 Would I repurchase? No – not because it’s bad, but because there’s so much more to explore in this space.

— Mrs. International Shraddha Vadalia 2024
